showpageafterlogin Plugin for DokuWiki

Redirects the user to a configureable page after login.
You can configure if this should happen every time or
for a specific amount of Logins (for Instruction/New User Pages)

All documentation for this plugin can be found at
https://www.dokuwiki.org/plugin:showpageafterlogin

Sources can be found at
https://github.com/s-blu/showpageafterlogin

----
If you install this plugin manually, make sure it is installed in
lib/plugins/showpageafterlogin/ - if the folder is called different it
will not work!

Please refer to http://www.dokuwiki.org/plugins for additional info
on how to install plugins in DokuWiki.

